// Workspace wiring the mobile build to the belphegor core.
//
// The core is vendored as a git submodule at ./belphegor (pinned commit). The
// gomobile facade and the android clipboard backend live in ./glue and are
// overlaid onto the submodule by scripts/setup-core.sh before building: they
// must sit inside the belphegor module to import its internal/* packages, but
// they are NOT part of the upstream core repo.
//
// After cloning:  git submodule update --init && scripts/setup-core.sh
go 1.26

use ./belphegor
